<paragraph blockId="6.[2006,2599,1677,2104]" pageId="6" pageNumber="167">
[northeast] Madagascar, 16°51°’S 49°08’E, in primary rainforest, between 600-750 metres altitude.” 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jenkins" authorityYear="1992" box="[2007,2209,1873,1906]" class="Mammalia" family="Tenrecidae" genus="Microgale" kingdom="Animalia" order="Afrosoricida" pageId="6" pageNumber="167" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dryas">Microgale dryas</taxonomicName>
